<HEADLINE> Shanghai Shenhua Beats Dutch Club in Soccer Contest </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 5 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai Shenhua converted a late
penalty kick for a 1-0 victory over visiting Feyenoord Rotterdam
of the Netherlands here Thursday in the Sino-Dutch soccer contest.
</P>
<P>
With three minutes to go, the local squad succeeded in its
counter off-side tactics. Foreign entry Peres of France made a
solo run to intercept the ball before being fouled in the penalty
box.
