</P>
<P>
Carr commented amid concern by environmental campaigners
Greenpeace over the discovery of rusting drum loads of the highly
toxic chemical, dioxin, in an area adjoining the site.
</P>
<P>
Earlier this week, Greenpeace activists protested about the
dioxin problem outside the headquarters of the International
Olympic Committee in Switzerland. 
</P>
