Armed Forces Chief Gen. Ismail Omar and Chief of Staff Gen. Nawi
Alias, and Deputy Inspector-General of Police Norian Mai.
</P>
<P>
Earlier today before the meeting, Malaysian Acting Prime
Minister Anwar Ibrahim called on the visiting Thai prime minister
and the two leaders discussed regional and international issues of
mutual concern, according to official sources.  
