coordinating body for environmental affairs and promote
environmentally sound and sustainable development in the country.
</P>
<P>
Myanmar adopted a national environment policy in late 1994 with
the aim of achieving harmony and balance between the environment
and development through the integration of environmental
consideration into the development process to enhance the quality
of the life of all its citizens.  
