the Commonwealth of Independent States (CIS) market, and also in
the European Union market.
</P>
<P>
The two-way trade volume between the two countries reached 2.45
million U.S. dollars in 1996, of which Hungary's export volume was
2.1 million dollars.
</P>
<P>
Ciubuc arrived in Hungary on June 3 for his two-day official
visit. 
