experienced drivers Ari Vatanen and Pier Lartigue will star in the
rally.
</P>
<P>
World motor manufacturing giants Mercedes, BMW, Mitsubisi,
Honda and Peugot are among the challengers.
</P>
<P>
Prizemoney for the rally will be 65,000 pounds (100,000
U.S. dollars). 
