Wednesday as profit worries intensified, weighing down the stock
market on Wall Street as investors braced for new clues on
inflation in Friday's key employment report.
</P>
<P>
The Dow Jones industrial average fell 42.49 points to 7,269.66.
</P>
<P>
There was limited reaction to news that factory orders
rebounded a bigger-than-expected 1.2 percent in April.
</P>
