the NYSE composite index fell 2.18 to 440.18, pulling back from
Tuesday's record close.
</P>
<P>
The Nasdaq composite index fell 5.24 to 1,379.67, and the
American Stock Exchange composite index fell 1.29 to 607.73.
</P>
<P>
Among major technology shares, IBM, Gateway, Compaq Computer,
Dell Computer and Intel continued to stumble. 
